{"id": "1445623099348484176", "channel_id": "1445623099348484176", "type": 0, "author_id": "1167548191441424425", "author_name": "null_0195", "author_bot": false, "content": "开一楼搬运一下贴吧用户@月之森银庭沙龙 的角色原型整理。感觉ta的版本比较全，方便大家检索（\n—————————以下是正文————————\n今天突然有点心血来潮，之前了解过一点\n\u0000三旧神先来\n\u0000【科普都是百度整理的】\n\u0000塔薇‖犹格索托斯\n\u0000形象为聚集着的无穷光辉球体。\n\u0000犹格·索托斯被视为时空的支配者和万物归一者，他的本体位于所有多维宇宙之外。犹格·索托斯拥有无穷的智慧，所有伟大的巫师、艺术家、思想家都是他在不同维度中的投影。有时，一些穿越终极之门去面见他的人会得到其知识。", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T03:50:05.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445623099562266754", "filename": "8493DE0ED92BB857BEDF57A24854F6F8.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 30201, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445623099562266754/8493DE0ED92BB857BEDF57A24854F6F8.jpg?ex=69cc95ed&is=69cb446d&hm=2844e6fb046cba5ad855e8c9432ecd07e26b611920e3db26645f153eb95382ad&"}, {"id": "1445623100107391088", "filename": "A20E56F27C40423F44B144A7EA8BC9ED.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 55459, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445623100107391088/A20E56F27C40423F44B144A7EA8BC9ED.jpg?ex=69cc95ed&is=69cb446d&hm=fc008b7f9c41c3ef2d15095ff43f86e4f983c5a91d3fdf17abac1e7a5dcbd307&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445623099348484176", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "各角色原型考据", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1445623328051171328", "channel_id": "1445623099348484176", "type": 0, "author_id": "1167548191441424425", "author_name": "null_0195", "author_bot": false, "content": "泰旖丝‖森之黑山羊莎布尼古拉斯\n她是万物之母，生命和生殖能力的根本，同时她本身也是一位拥有超强生殖力的神。其形象在洛夫克拉夫特的信件中仅描绘为“云雾般的存在”，后经由后人完善为黑云般的巨大肉块，有着许多触手和羊蹄，以及滴着黏液的大嘴。", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T03:50:59.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445623327011115139", "filename": "00FBD54CEEF776B73BF789447BCEA8C9.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 26117, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445623327011115139/00FBD54CEEF776B73BF789447BCEA8C9.jpg?ex=69cc9623&is=69cb44a3&hm=fe1853e86cb28bcda976ff0ef4180358caa80fa3acfdbde3468f0f7d15dca33c&"}, {"id": "1445623327614828670", "filename": "338ADC326AE0424547D72C33E21C9826.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 124219, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445623327614828670/338ADC326AE0424547D72C33E21C9826.jpg?ex=69cc9623&is=69cb44a3&hm=27b67c388fd0b908453b75f11024929ff915858006b9ba31b9ad316cabe166f6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445623099348484176", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "各角色原型考据", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1445623494829277228", "channel_id": "1445623099348484176", "type": 0, "author_id": "1167548191441424425", "author_name": "null_0195", "author_bot": false, "content": "N‖奈亚拉托提普\n他常化作人形在地球上行走，有时表现为一个有着深色皮肤、身材瘦削，模样看起来像是古埃及法老的人类。奈亚拉托提普热衷于欺骗、诱惑凡人，以使人类陷入恐怖与绝望到最终精神失常为其喜悦，但同时也受到米·戈、古革巨人、月兽、冷原人的崇拜。在克苏鲁神话中，他的形象最接近于传统“恶魔”的概念。\n常见称呼：【千面之神】【伏行之混沌】", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T03:51:39.553000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445623494590332968", "filename": "55D2947F4959CB161624DA0DB117BB19.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 36075, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445623494590332968/55D2947F4959CB161624DA0DB117BB19.jpg?ex=69cc964b&is=69cb44cb&hm=ea597f77ad50b4590e8f8e92c0beba25ab91b3bcadc09080cfb0b1618b779c36&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445623099348484176", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "各角色原型考据", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1445623881200304189", "channel_id": "1445623099348484176", "type": 0, "author_id": "1167548191441424425", "author_name": "null_0195", "author_bot": false, "content": "哈姆林‖特鲁宁布拉\n特鲁宁布拉是环绕阿撒托斯宫殿的无形吹奏者之一，在那里它为阿撒托斯演奏各种极其令人难忘的音乐，阿撒托斯的庭臣们在它的伴奏下围绕阿撒托斯翩翩起舞。活声波特鲁宁布拉没有实际的躯体，以声音的形式存在。它产生的声波可以穿透一切屏障，当面对它的时候，即使把耳朵堵上也无效，哪怕聋子也不能幸免。", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T03:53:11.671000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445623099348484176", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "各角色原型考据", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1445624040520810570", "channel_id": "1445623099348484176", "type": 0, "author_id": "1167548191441424425", "author_name": "null_0195", "author_bot": false, "content": "克莱门汀‖夏盖虫族【集合体】\n作为与阿撒托斯接触的结果，夏盖虫族拥有Kirlian Phasing的能力，它们能够直接穿行于其他生物的大脑之中。在地球上它们常常使用这种法术移动进人类的大脑之中，逐渐控制宿主的心智。", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T03:53:49.656000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445624039791005868", "filename": "25174A392D884F18D11E2263D47F2B85.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 109030, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445624039791005868/25174A392D884F18D11E2263D47F2B85.jpg?ex=69cc96cd&is=69cb454d&hm=cd1cf54ea91fe06a184976f790ecb5d92d71a44b5d459950ab83a6754155fd28&"}, {"id": "1445624040289992704", "filename": "7692F4ECD143725B70F3990E55D83A9D.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 83923, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445624040289992704/7692F4ECD143725B70F3990E55D83A9D.jpg?ex=69cc96cd&is=69cb454d&hm=f40375aebbfd579ad54c3771ee966b87ef3e46a3cd720c141e93c156b842fcab&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445623099348484176", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "各角色原型考据", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1445624253993979904", "channel_id": "1445623099348484176", "type": 0, "author_id": "1167548191441424425", "author_name": "null_0195", "author_bot": false, "content": "【偏主观】\n神父‖乌波·萨斯拉➕伊格（元素偏少）\n乌波·萨斯拉\n它是一个巨大的原生质体，由不属于这个宇宙的物质构成。它没有任何固定的形状，无数的原质体生物在它体表蠕动。乌波·萨斯拉守卫的石碑一直是巫师们寻求的。\n伊格\n蛇之父，形象为长满鳞片的半蛇半人。在美洲广为流传，被北美和中美原住民称作“众蛇之父”和“坏药”的蛇之祖神。首次出场于H.P.洛夫克拉夫特&齐里亚·毕夏普做著《伊格的诅咒》中。\ntips：伊格的复仇元素太过强烈我觉得明显不应是属于神父的主要原型。可是祂的尾部其实是很暧昧不清的节状，菱状的尾巴背部很明显就属于两栖类的，和其所谓“变形虫”的外形有冲突。", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T03:54:40.552000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445624252182036591", "filename": "9BA72C1106B9E0FE24A664B354C8DE4E.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 47101, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445624252182036591/9BA72C1106B9E0FE24A664B354C8DE4E.jpg?ex=69cc9700&is=69cb4580&hm=9f52172ee622cb106df95c4c500e91cb587a4eb36d8f5740bf304193c6400628&"}, {"id": "1445624252739883098", "filename": "80756DB6E638C9B37E4B55A4CF08B8B8.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 37493, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445624252739883098/80756DB6E638C9B37E4B55A4CF08B8B8.jpg?ex=69cc9700&is=69cb4580&hm=0759f2e5de9c88f51c589e3f892a21827a7fb5bc71e5992c2bc924c87b62b03f&"}, {"id": "1445624253343993939", "filename": "FCC23D864746858153CC4BE1D585C86C.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 126435, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445623099348484176/1445624253343993939/FCC23D864746858153CC4BE1D585C86C.jpg?ex=69cc9700&is=69cb4580&hm=fef8448bdafd8683fe58cf9935a3ceb0262dfbbc81d3b7011b74c7ac5cf8c6cf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445623099348484176", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "各角色原型考据", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
